front.title: Patrol Craft
front.gametext: Power +1 at Coruscant or Bespin. May add 1 driver and 1 passenger. May deploy or move as a 'react.' At cloud sectors, may move and be targeted by weapons like a starfighter.
front.lore: Small, enclosed patrol fighter used on many worlds to help maintain order. A cheaper alternative to the Bespin Motors cloud car.
